1. *Pritiska* me ova situacija. (This situation is *pressing* on me.)
2. Ne mogu da *pritiskam* dugme, jako je tvrdo. (I can't *press* the button, it's very hard.)
3. On *pritiska* svoju devojku da se uda za njega. (He's *pressuring* his girlfriend to marry him.)
4. Niska temperatura može *pritiskati* naš organizam. (Low temperature can *put pressure on* our body.)
5. Moramo *pritiskati* vladu da reši ovaj problem. (We need to *put pressure on* the government to solve this problem.)
6. Kada me nervira, ona *pritiska* svoje olovke na papir. (When she gets on my nerves, she *presses* her pen onto the paper.)
7. Treba da izbegavamo da *pritiskamo* rane jer to može da izazove infekciju. (We should avoid *pressing* on wounds because it can cause infection.)
8. Vozač je *pritiskao* kočnicu, ali automobil nije stao. (The driver *pressed* the brake, but the car didn't stop.)
9. Ova vest će *pritiskati* akcije na berzi. (This news will *put pressure on* the stocks at the exchange.)
10. Ne bi trebalo da *pritiskamo* decu da postignu savršenstvo. (We shouldn't *pressure* children to achieve perfection.)